data.description: Check out this practically new house, only 4 years new.  NO HOA!  Three bedrooms and two full baths upstairs, first floor laundry.  Large finished private retreat with bedroom, full bath, and an office in the lower level.  Great area to relax and enjoy.   Beautiful spacious kitchen with large quartz island, quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances.  Covered deck with multiple layers and nice fenced back yard with wooded views.
